{"type":"message","id":"2b508993","parentId":"33038b14","timestamp":"2026-04-24T09:33:04.542Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is pointing out a valid concern - they've been doing daily reviews and I keep re-analyzing all feedback which leads to duplicate work. They want me to check if the P0-P2 features I proposed are already implemented in the current version (v4.8.0) before proposing them again.\n\nLet me check the current SKILL.md and scripts to verify what's actually implemented.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"说得对，让我先核查一下本地 v4.8.0 的实际实现情况。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_trc5iqssqv06_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"SKILL_DIR=\"/workspace/projects/extensions/coze-openclaw-plugin/skills/healthcheck\"\necho \"=== 脚本列表 ===\"\nls \"$SKILL_DIR/scripts/\"\necho \"\"\necho \"=== SKILL.md 关键词检查 ===\"\ngrep -n -E \"(定时|scheduled|cron|定时扫描|定时巡检|自动巡检|自动扫描|告警|alert|notification)\" \"$SKILL_DIR/SKILL.md\" | head -30\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 查找 wizard/交互引导 ===\"\nls \"$SKILL_DIR/scripts/\" | grep -E \"(wizard|interactive|guide)\"\necho \"\"\necho \"=== 查找 smart fix 相关 ===\"\ngrep -rn \"fix-smart\\|smart.*fix\\|智能.*修复\" \"$SKILL_DIR/\" 2>/dev/null | head -10\necho \"\"\necho \"=== references 目录 ===\"\nls \"$SKILL_DIR/references/\" 2>/dev/null || echo \"无 references 目录\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":58887,"output":401,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59288,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777023172834,"responseId":"063a6bc558466d95f21866cd24ff8606"}}
